<![endif]-->  <p class="MsoNormal">&nbsp;</p><lj-cut text="Clich&eacute;'d"><p class="MsoNormal"><b style=""><span style="font-size: 16pt;">Clich&eacute;&rsquo;d.<o:p></o:p></span></b></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-I&rsquo;m not <i style="">stalking</i> you!</span><span lang="EN-US" style=""> It&rsquo;s</span><span lang="EN-GB" style=""> just&hellip;<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">Gretchen didn&rsquo;t know an easy way to tell Claire the truth. What she <i style="">did</i> know was that she was going to lose her if she kept acting like that.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">She was on the verge of tears.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-Gretchen? Just <i style="">what</i>?<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">The taller girl fixed her gaze on Claire&rsquo;s eyes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">This was gonna be bad. Really bad. But she couldn&rsquo;t keep everything inside anymore.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">It was now or never.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">She sighed heavily, then she took a step forward.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">In the next few moments everything happened so fast, that Claire wasn&rsquo;t really able to tell how Gretchen&rsquo;s lips ended up gently kissing hers.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">Let&rsquo;s be clear, It wasn&rsquo;t that mind-blowing breath-taking legs-melting kind of kiss. It was just a simple kiss, and it lasted no more than two or three second. Yet, it was enough to send a shiver down her spine. Enough to leave her shocked and without a single word to say. <o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">Gretchen&rsquo;s eyes were a bit teary, but she had a small smile gracing her lips. Lips that a few moments ago were on hers. Claire was practically goggling at her.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">The brunette took a step back, but didn&rsquo;t stop looking into Claire&rsquo;s eyes.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-I..I kinda have a ginormous crush for you, Claire. I&rsquo;m so sorry. I just didn&rsquo;t want to freak you out, and ruin whatever it was we were building.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-I&hellip;emh&hellip;I- <o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">Claire looked a bit overwhelmed.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-It&rsquo;s okay, it&rsquo;s not like I expected you to actually return my feelings or anything.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">She laughed nervously, fidgeting with her fingers.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">The blonde sat down on the bed behind her.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">She needed a minute to wrap her mind around the fact that she actually&hellip;<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-Liked it. I liked it. <o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">She whispered to herself quietly.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-What?<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><i style=""><span lang="EN-GB" style="">I kissed a girl and I liked it</span></i><span lang="EN-GB" style="">. She half-smiled.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">How <i style="">clich&eacute;</i>. She shook her head in amusement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">Gretchen took a step forward and sit and on the very edge of the bed.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-Do you want me to move out?<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">She kept her voice low. <o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">Claire looked like she was doing some serious meditation. Which was&hellip;well, strange. She was smiling most of the time, but now her expression was between serious and amazed. <o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">The brunette could almost hear her brain <i style="">puffing and panting</i>. <o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-Claire?<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">The girl in question closed her eyes for a second.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-Gretchen, I&rsquo;m&hellip;confused right now. <o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-I can underst-<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">When she opened her eyes again, she smiled lightly.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-But no, I don&rsquo;t want you to move out.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">Gretchen breathed away the air she couldn&rsquo;t remember she had been holding.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">Claire gently brushed her cheek with her fingers. <i style="">When did she get that close?</i><o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-And now, I want to try something.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">She whispered, her breath on Gretchen&rsquo;s lips.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">The girl froze. <i style="">What&rsquo;s happening?<o:p></o:p></i></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">She couldn&rsquo;t think straight. Not with Claire that close to her. To her lips. Well, actually she was never able to think straight when she was with Claire. She was amazing.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">And now she was sitting there, less than a breath away from her mouth. She couldn&rsquo;t take it.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-Claire- The whisper died on the soft lips of the blonde when she kissed her.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">It wasn&rsquo;t like the one from a minute before. It was a soft caressing of lips, a light touching of tongues. Claire&rsquo;s left hand went up, sliding under Gretchen&rsquo;s hair, stroking the back of her neck, the right still cupping her cheek, while Gretchen&rsquo;s hands let themselves fall on Claire&rsquo;s hips. <o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">It was&hellip;incredible.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">It wasn&rsquo;t like Claire had never kissed anyone. Hell, she kissed plenty of boys before. But kissing a girl, kissing Gretchen, was such a different experience. It was like she was in a fairy tale. She would probably be lifting her right foot right now, if she was standing.<span style="">&nbsp; </span>Because she was corny like that.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">When the kiss ended, the blondie rested her forehead on the crook of the other girl&rsquo;s neck, hiding a small smile. <o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">Gretchen was amused.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-Superpowers, excellent taste in book and a good kisser. You kinda left out this last part.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-Yeah, didn&rsquo;t think it was that important anyway. Or that you cared, for all that matters.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">Gretchen blushed and was about to reply something when Claire pulled away her head from her neck. Though, she noticed, the girl didn&rsquo;t break the physical contact between them, only sliding her right hand on the side of her neck.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">The brunette was practically beaming. Claire thought she was so cute with that goofy smile of hers.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-So, <i style="">Supergirl</i>, wanna give it a try?<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">Claire smirked and then assumed the most innocent face she could manage, though the mischievous look in her eyes was betraying her. She murmured slowly:<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-I have never done this before. <o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">Gretchen laughed softly. <o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">-Well, I would hope not.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">She breathed in reply before going for Claire&rsquo;s lips for the second time that evening.<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">An evening they sure hadn&rsquo;t planned to go that way.<span style="">&nbsp; </span><o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">But hey, college is about reinventing yourself, right?<o:p></o:p></span></p>  <p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="EN-GB" style="">And no one was going to complain, anyway. <o:p></o:p></span></p></lj-cut><br /><br /></meta></meta></meta></meta>
